{"tid":2086088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：「外部勢力搞亂香港」藍絲紀錄片獲希臘電影節最佳外語短片獎 不過期後發現今日才截止提名","createTime":"2020-06-30T07:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T07:39:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1c22c9f000546b2d5c823407117a6524b6466e","tid":2086088,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"近日有傳媒報道，一部斥反送中是「外部勢力搞亂香港」的 15 分鐘紀錄片，獲「希臘耶拉派特拉國際紀錄片電影節最佳外語短片獎」，得到評審團「高度評價」。不過《立場新聞》調查發現， 該電影節疑團重重。涉事電影於 6 月 21 日獲獎，但電影節卻於今日（6 月 30 日）才截止報名。此外，這個「最佳外語短片獎」，本來更是不存在於電影節獎項清單。<br />\n<br />\n涉事紀錄片名為《香港，請再次閃耀》，英文名為 Hong Kong - Please shining again，由中國紀錄片導演金華青製作。長約 15 分鐘的影片批評外國勢力介入香港事務，稱反送中是「外部勢力在搞亂香港」，並提及多名政治人物，包括黃之鋒、黎智英、李柱銘等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E7%AF%80-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87%E7%8D%B2%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%8D%8E-%E5%A0%B1%E5%90%8D%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%AA%E5%AE%8C%E5%B7%B2%E9%A0%92%E7%8D%8E-%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E5%A4%96%E8%AA%9E%E7%89%87%E7%8D%8E-%E6%9C%AC%E4%BE%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8/#.XvrkluRgGLs.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25A5%2587%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%258D%258E-%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%25A0%2592%25E7%258D%258E-%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25AA%259E%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%258D%258E-%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AD%2598%25E5%259C%25A8%2F%23.XvrkluRgGLs.facebook&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=2c8b138e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcultur